riginally published Figure 3 is shown here for reference:</p><fig id="fig2" position="float"><graphic mimetype="image" mime-subtype="tiff" xlink:href="elife-98284-fig2-v1.tif"/></fig><p>The reviewers approved the new images in corrected Figure 3. The article has been corrected accordingly.</p></body></article>